<section class="panel">
  <h2>✍️ Salvation Essay Structure</h2>

  <p class="lead">
    Use this scaffold to help structure your written response using KJV Scripture,
    analysis, and personal reflection.
  </p>

  <div class="scripture">
    <strong>Core Focus</strong>
    <p>
      Explain what the Bible teaches about salvation, how it changes identity and lifestyle,
      and how believers are called to live through the power of the Holy Ghost.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- INTRODUCTION -->
  <div class="slide-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">INTRODUCTION</p>

    <h3>Define Salvation, Faith, and Scripture</h3>

    <ul class="slide-points">
      <li>Define salvation according to the Bible.</li>
      <li>Explain why the Word of God is the authority.</li>
      <li>Introduce key concepts:
        faith, repentance, baptism, Holy Ghost, holiness, endurance.
      </li>
      <li>Include at least one KJV scripture.</li>
    </ul>

    <textarea
      data-save="essay-introduction"
      placeholder="Write your introduction here..."></textarea>
  </div>

  <!-- PARAGRAPH 1 -->
  <div class="slide-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">PARAGRAPH 1</p>

    <h3>Analyse the Problem of Sin</h3>

    <ul class="slide-points">
      <li>Explain creation and the fall.</li>
      <li>Analyse how sin separates humanity from God.</li>
      <li>Explain why every person needs salvation.</li>
      <li>Use KJV scripture evidence.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="scripture">
      <strong>Suggested Scriptures</strong>
      <p>
        Genesis 1:27 • Romans 5:12 • Romans 3:23 • Romans 6:23
      </p>
    </div>

    <textarea
      data-save="essay-paragraph1"
      placeholder="Write paragraph 1 here..."></textarea>
  </div>

  <!-- PARAGRAPH 2 -->
  <div class="slide-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">PARAGRAPH 2</p>

    <h3>Analyse God’s Solution Through Jesus Christ</h3>

    <ul class="slide-points">
      <li>Explain the Old Testament sacrifice pattern.</li>
      <li>Explain Jesus as God manifest in the flesh.</li>
      <li>Analyse the cross and resurrection.</li>
      <li>Explain why Jesus has authority to forgive and remove sin.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="scripture">
      <strong>Suggested Scriptures</strong>
      <p>
        Hebrews 9:22 • Hebrews 10:4 • John 1:14 •
        1 Timothy 3:16 • 1 Peter 2:24 • Matthew 28:6
      </p>
    </div>

    <textarea
      data-save="essay-paragraph2"
      placeholder="Write paragraph 2 here..."></textarea>
  </div>

  <!-- PARAGRAPH 3 -->
  <div class="slide-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">PARAGRAPH 3</p>

    <h3>Analyse the Biblical Plan of Salvation</h3>

    <ul class="slide-points">
      <li>Explain faith from the Word of God.</li>
      <li>Explain repentance.</li>
      <li>Explain baptism in Jesus’ name.</li>
      <li>Explain receiving the Holy Ghost.</li>
      <li>Explain holiness and endurance.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="scripture">
      <strong>Suggested Scriptures</strong>
      <p>
        Romans 10:17 • Acts 2:38 • Acts 1:8 •
        1 Peter 1:16 • Matthew 24:13
      </p>
    </div>

    <textarea
      data-save="essay-paragraph3"
      placeholder="Write paragraph 3 here..."></textarea>
  </div>

  <!-- PARAGRAPH 4 -->
  <div class="slide-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">PARAGRAPH 4</p>

    <h3>Personal Reflection and Application</h3>

    <ul class="slide-points">
      <li>Reflect on how biblical salvation affects life today.</li>
      <li>Explain how the Holy Ghost gives power to overcome sin.</li>
      <li>Reflect on holiness, obedience, and endurance.</li>
      <li>Connect scripture to personal application.</li>
    </ul>

    <textarea
      data-save="essay-paragraph4"
      placeholder="Write your reflection here..."></textarea>
  </div>

  <!-- CONCLUSION -->
  <div class="slide-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">CONCLUSION</p>

    <h3>Summarise the Message of Salvation</h3>

    <ul class="slide-points">
      <li>Restate the problem of sin.</li>
      <li>Summarise God’s solution through Jesus Christ.</li>
      <li>Summarise the Acts 2:38 response.</li>
      <li>End with a final reflective statement.</li>
    </ul>

    <textarea
      data-save="essay-conclusion"
      placeholder="Write your conclusion here..."></textarea>
  </div>

  <!-- CHECKLIST -->
  <div class="panel challenge-box">
    <h2>✅ Essay Checklist</h2>

    <ul class="slide-points">
      <li>☐ Defined key biblical concepts</li>
      <li>☐ Used KJV Scripture references</li>
      <li>☐ Analysed the problem of sin</li>
      <li>☐ Explained Jesus’ role in salvation</li>
      <li>☐ Explained Acts 2:38</li>
      <li>☐ Connected salvation with identity and behaviour</li>
      <li>☐ Included personal reflection</li>
      <li>☐ Used analytical language</li>
      <li>☐ Explained holiness and endurance</li>
      <li>☐ Used evidence to support ideas</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>